{
  "stem": "868.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He walked in the hesitating little steps.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He had to be helped by somebody else all the time, so this trip for him, all the way to where we were was, quite an ordeal.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The relationship with him during the orphanage-- my stay at the orphanage became very close and very warm.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I even was [CHUCKLES] promoted to his personal barber.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So twice a week, it was my job to shave him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was very conscious of this situation, because he was highly respected, not just at the orphanage, naturally, and in the area of Florence where we were-- Rifredi-- but all throughout Florence.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was considered a saint.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was conscious of this situation where a Jewish refugee boy shaving an eminent priest of the Catholic Church in a very cozy relationship.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I made my way back to the orphanage.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He went on to the farmhouse to see if he could retrieve some of the other boys.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But he was told, don't worry.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They're going to work in factories in German-- in Germany.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They'll be safe.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Fact is that only three of them returned-- of this entire group-- later.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remained in the orphanage with Willy [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] until the liberation of Florence, which happened-- Florence being considered a special case because of its art treasures.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As the Germans retreated, they blew up all the bridges across the Arno River except the famous Ponte Vecchio, which goes back to the 17th century.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they blew up the houses on both sides of the famous bridge so it could not be used.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We at the orphanage [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] had heard the cannons all throughout the nights and so forth, but we had not seen any Allied troops yet.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
